&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Any Festival is an occasion to celebrate.&lt;br>
If the day is Vijaya Dashami&lt;br>
Then the day is to&lt;br>
Celebrate your success (Vijay)&lt;br>
Celebrate your journey&lt;br>
Celebrate your learning through a tough time&lt;br>
Otherwise, many people quit on the way.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shanti Patha - शान्तिपाठः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shanti-paath/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/shanti-paath/</guid><description>&lt;p>
